- A) Low Energy Display
- B) Light Emitting Diode
- C) Liquid Electron Device
- D) Linear Energy Distribution

## Question 5
What does "pH" stand for in chemistry?
- A) Potential Hydrogen
- B) Partial Hydration
- C) Power of Hydrogen
- D) Positive Hydroxide

Good luck!

